aces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到篇文就覺得好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802281a444cbf4c3c8f2a68b7cffbeead3994d05","tid":884340,"uid":70040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c0372e6f3cd6dd79b5bc9b07aa44a944da802b","tid":884340,"uid":167464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"連鏗哥都畀你擺埋上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，如果無鏗哥當年篇文，我都無鬥志走後門入hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到篇文就覺得好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"篇文長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改得勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}